{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":913132,"duration_api_ms":897279,"num_turns":175,"result":"The implementation is complete. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n**PR #9676 - Fix `get_url` for subrepos:**\n- `dvc/api/data.py`: Rewrote `get_url()` to use the subrepo's index storage directly (via `index.storage_map.get_remote(entry)`) instead of going through `dvcfs.info()` and `cloud.get_url_for()`, which didn't correctly resolve remotes for subrepos.\n- `dvc/fs/dvc.py`: Added `ExitStack` for proper subrepo lifecycle management, added `md5-dos2unix` to `_merge_info()`, and added `close()` methods to both `_DVCFileSystem` and `DVCFileSystem`.\n- `dvc/repo/__init__.py`: Added `dvcfs.close()` calls in `close()` and `_reset()`.\n- `dvc/repo/open_repo.py`: Added `url = os.path.abspath(url)` to normalize paths.\n\n**PR #9718 - Add `--type` to `fetch`:**\n- `dvc/commands/data_sync.py`: Added `--type` argument with `metrics`/`plots` choices and passes `types` to `repo.fetch()`.\n- `dvc/repo/fetch.py`: Added `types` parameter to the `fetch()` function signature and passes it to `targets_view()`.\n- `dvc/repo/index.py`: Added `metric_keys` and `plot_keys` cached properties, `_types_filter()` method, and updated `targets_view()` to accept and filter by `types`.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"665b7e52-f518-4331-b9d6-f3bcfe6540b8","total_cost_usd":25.776723900000004,"usage":{"input_tokens":8112833,"cache_creation_input_tokens":776,"cache_read_input_tokens":636314,"output_tokens":42110,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"cache_deleted_input_tokens":0,"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed":{"inputTokens":8313669,"outputTokens":42554,"cacheReadInputTokens":648323,"cacheCreationInputTokens":776,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":25.776723900000004,"